Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seven-colored dusk descended{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wind is somewhat cool{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saturday night is lively{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even a gloomy feeling is soon cleared up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And everyone is getting excited{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go DOWN TOWN{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go DOWN TOWN{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go DOWN TOWN{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.10,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.\NIt's packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the front rows are packed.\NWe've got people sitting all the way to the front row.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys are looking forward to Shimashimans after us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimashimans is the last performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-  I didn't know that.\N- I thought you guys were waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san is very excited at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.\N- We all have those energetic annoying uncles right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose you go out for dinner with your relatives and get harassed by a thug.\NAnd when that happens, your uncle is surprisingly not doing anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not that guy.\N- I am very lazy to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredibly many juniors are watching us at the side of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told to do something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a legendary comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm charismatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get rid of my charisma by taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get rid of my charisma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like a tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- They said to do it, so let's do it.\N- Yeah, we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- What was that like again?\N- What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean manzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't done that for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and Hamada-san said that we only do manzai for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's a good idea.\NBut you got rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- I see.\N- That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried you were not going to do this because you're rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have more money than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absolutely not true!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you talking about!?\N- That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You DEFINITELY have more money than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone come out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did we do in our manzai?\N- We did a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Audience: Kidnapping one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\NHe is this kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He often shit talks everytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done kidnapping one and doctor one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Audience: Researchers one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So who the hell are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that twice, you're persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we also did ghost one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, the ghost one?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And the quiz one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a quiz once in a while, just to warm up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- What should I do?\N- Well, let's do a quiz to warm up. Then give me a common quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.\NWe are a duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were a trio and Yanagida-kun was here, I would have asked him to do it.\NBut there is no Yanagida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only Matsumoto and Hamada.\NIt can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a common quiz.\NHmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whatever.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How many meters is Tokyo Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How many meters is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How many meters is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"How many meters?"\NHey, this is a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So how many meters is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you the quiz and I have to give you the answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.18,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of you.\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me to give you a quiz, so I gave you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are you asking me to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so I'm supposed to give you the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For that matter, what is the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 333 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "this is tough"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is more than tough, it's heartbreaking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Heartbreaking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be heartbreaking !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just asked a question and gave the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We came all the way to NGK(Namba Grand kagetsu) today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's why I don't want to fight with you.\N- Fight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We are graduates of NSC.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the first generation of New Star Creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We should not be fighting at NGK.\NAll right, that's enough, Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you mean by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the Tokyo Tower is 333 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that tall.\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you so much.\N- What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send flowers to your dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is 333 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "it's not that tall"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that because it's not that tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that because it's 333 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is 333 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I might embarrass you because I said this.\NCan I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived by the Tokyo Tower for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- I lived there for two years and renewed my lease.\N- You renewed yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I lived there for two years and a half.\NWhen I woke up in the morning and looked out the window, I could see Tokyo Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was it that close?\N- I used to look at Tokyo Tower from my window every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- There were days when the windows were covered with lace curtains.\N- I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if there were lace curtains on the windows, I could still see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the lace curtains was only slightly open, I could see it from there.\NSo I could see it almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so I say that it's not that tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry. I'm so sorry!\N- No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Does your stomach hurt?\N- I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, his name is Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's playing a rough character.\NI wish you could at least remember his name and face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know it's not 333 meters long just by looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, Hamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's officially stated to be 333 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's 333 meters tall.\N- No, it's not that tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it, and I'm telling you, I'm absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you only looked at it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What you see is all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what are YOU saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're scaring me.\N- Okay, how tall do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not 333 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know the right answer to know that someone is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, suppose someone suddenly says, "Hello," and you reply, "Hello,".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is obvious that person is not Shoei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this guy talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And he is an elementary school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so fed up, I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to know the right answer to know that someone is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you only looked at it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.\NWhat's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I be nervous!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nervous about the live viewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, let's take it slow.\NLet's do it so you don't get nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't want you to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.71,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,we're getting nowhere with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally I don't want to get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So how tall do you think it is?\NJust tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It is officially 333 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you didn't know the right answer.\NBut if you saw it every day, how many meters would you guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,200...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,200?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,More than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"More than"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"More than 200"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the kind of symbol.\N(200～)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a chance that your 333 meters is correct, too!\NAfter all, that's MORE THAN 200!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sorry if you were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, that thing is 333 meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- But...\N- 200 KARA (More than 200)?\N"KARA"(more than)?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how they say,\N"Yakyu - wa - 2 out - YAKARA".\N(Because baseball is two outs)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yakyu - wa - 2 out - YAKARA".\N(Because baseball is two outs)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yakyu - wa - 2 out - YAKARA".\N(Because baseball is two outs)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Baseball starts...\N- Once, in a public bath, an older man was watching TV and said, "Yakyu - wa - 2 out - YAKARA".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, no, no...\N- "Go for it! The game is about to begin!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's\N"Yakyu - wa - 2 out - KARAYAKARA."\N(Baseball starts with 2 outs.)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, It's "Yakyu - wa - 2 out - YAKARA".\N(Because  baseball is two outs)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Daijoubu - ya! Yakyu - wa - 2 out - KARAYAKARA", right?\N(Don't worry! Baseball starts with 2 outs.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much KARA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's kind of too long.\N- I don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you the one who brought it up?!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.\N"NGK YAKARA".\N(Because this is NGK.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That' s enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's okay.\N- What's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait a moment.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's why you're nervous, right?\N- No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you didn't talk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tiresome to have a meeting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about what you're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but we're doing this now, so why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're a great guy.\N- You're the only one having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For a middle-aged man, you're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay. So do you know how tall Mt. Fuji?\N- Are you going to continue this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how tall Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how tall Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody knows how tall Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,3,77...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,(5? 6?)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,About 3,776.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 3,776 meters?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for....real!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why couldn't you guess the height of Tokyo Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.\NI saw it from a distance on the  bullet tarain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know the height just from this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it from a distance and that's how I knew how tall it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a great spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never climbed Mt. Fuji, but even if I had, I wouldn't know how tall it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rainbow Bridge is beautiful, but you would never know it by crossing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Disneyland is not something you see from a distance, but you don't know how fun it is until you go there.\N- That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you want?\N- That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if I end up with this.\NBut this is why you get angry when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to solve that right now. This is why you always get angry when you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eliminate uneasiness here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't get angry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make you feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be offended if I tell you this.\NYou are not the type to give quizzes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been quizzing me all along, so you should be the one quizzing me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You only told me, "Think of one or two common quizzes."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"So that's it!?", I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you keep talking about whatever comes to your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if I'm a grown man like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're not the quizzing type.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:17:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three types of people: those who give quizzes, those who don't give quizzes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who don't use comforters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Was that funny?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then let's do it.\N- Hey, are you still going to continue this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why do you want to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a quiz, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you want to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm doing it because I have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me a decent quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Munch's Scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, It's a picture of a man with his mouth wide open, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Munch himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:18:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- You think Munch is screaming because he has his mouth open.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you look closely at the painting, you will see that Munch is covering his ears with his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's titled "Scream," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He is covering his ears because someone is screamng too loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not "Munch's scream," but really "Munch is being screamed at."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer is "Munch is being shouted at."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't quiz me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't quiz me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just talking to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to read the room!\NYou have to read between the lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is that kind of quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say, "He is covering his ears..." answer "Munch is being screamed at"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is that kind of quiz.\N- I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new type of quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,New types are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,(*The sound of an incorrect answer)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.\NYou still want to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you know what a bullet train's bar is?\N- What bar are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, bullet train's bar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where's the bar you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it to you now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me quickly!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWhy are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I'm not.\N- Is it a hormonal problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Something wrong with your hormones?\N- No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you not feeling well?\N- I'm feeling fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are all your teeth hurting?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all your teeth hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say my teeth hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all your teeth hurting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, you should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the bar that you can grab in the men's restroom of the bullet train.\N- Yeah, I know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- You were talking about that bar.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that bar is the dirtiest bar in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone grabs it with the hand that touched their dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be pee on their hands when the train arrived at Mikawa-Anjo station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be grabbing that bar with their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:21:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I grabbed that bar, I wouldn't want to put my dick in my pants with my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That bar is even dirtier than dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how dirty I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked others if they would grab that bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They all said, "I never touch that stick because it's dirty."\NNobody touches that bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's the cleanest bar in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I did!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding dong!\N"That's the cleanest stick!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the room!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the nervousness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's hard.\N- No, it's not hard at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's very hard for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fake-Hamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to give me a quiz, give me a decent quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well...\N- Hey, has the quiz started yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- There was a cafe.\N- Is that a quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- There used to be  a cafe called Rika in the neighborhood of Nippon TV in Kojimachi.\N- Is that a quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cafe Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was looking at the Cafe RIKA(りか) signboard, I couldn't let my guard down while I was watching RI(リ).
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I am only looking at RI(リ).
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let my guard down until I see KA(カ).
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a curve with KA(か), RI(り) is hiragana!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:23:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But if there is no curve with KA(カ), it is katakana.\NSo you can't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say the same for both\NAichi(愛知)  and  Ehime(愛媛).
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't determine which is which by the first letter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, things should not be determined by the upper half of the body alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If an older man was in the bathtub, you still don't kno w if he is an older man or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If he stood up, he might be a centaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't determine things only by the upper half of their body!\NI would say don't determine things based on the first half alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- "Don't determine only by the first half."\N- Weren't we just talking about Rika?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cafe Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding dong!\N"Don't determine only by the first half!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to get 2 points for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of points before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we just talking about cafes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,0:24:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my line.\NWhat do YOU want?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.65,0:24:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(Are you crazy?)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.05,0:24:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I'm on a roll today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.29,0:24:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.93,0:24:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to solve that right now. This is why you get angry when you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.03,0:24:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep saying that, but I won't get angry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried that you'll get angry later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.61,0:24:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- You?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.31,0:24:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.25,0:24:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play the quiet-quiet game.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.62,0:24:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.56,0:25:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get points for being quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.76,0:25:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.07,0:25:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the right answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.97,0:25:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You get points for being quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.61,0:25:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.38,0:25:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How many home runs did Sadaharu Oh have in his professional baseball career?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.39,0:25:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,868.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.72,0:25:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you.\NThis is a quiet-quiet game.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.70,0:25:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.54,0:25:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right?\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's officially the quiet-quiet-quiet game.\N- I don't care about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.24,0:25:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's what I call it by abbreviation.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.81,0:26:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.58,0:26:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.81,0:26:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you nuts!?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.85,0:26:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You get points for being quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.65,0:26:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The points go up like rats reproducing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.29,0:26:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you talk, you'll lose more and more points.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.83,0:26:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.81,0:26:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's one thing I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.14,0:26:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.74,0:26:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.85,0:27:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.82,0:27:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.55,0:27:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.17,0:27:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How many liters are in a gallon?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.24,0:27:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A gallon...?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.08,0:27:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.92,0:27:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you concentrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.59,0:27:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.89,0:27:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your article going to be in next week's magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.06,0:27:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, I wouldn't be in such a good mood to do this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so set on yourself that it's a scandal?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.87,0:28:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way they would publish a good article about me in that one!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.61,0:28:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.94,0:28:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.18,0:28:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be quiet.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.21,0:28:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- All you have to do is be quiet.\N- I know!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.85,0:28:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.03,0:28:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.34,0:28:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.91,0:28:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.\NAh damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.75,0:28:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just shit my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.49,0:28:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow...I shit my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.56,0:28:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.23,0:28:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely shit my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:28:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.44,0:29:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.07,0:29:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.64,0:29:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.04,0:29:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.78,0:29:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.79,0:29:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.76,0:29:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You just say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.13,0:29:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a more clear-cut quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.43,0:29:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we are standing on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.41,0:29:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a three-choice quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.78,0:29:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Three choices?\N- Three choices is too hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.05,0:29:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're going to say something...\N- It would be hard with your stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.52,0:29:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.45,0:29:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're going to say something crazy to me again, so give me two choices.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.76,0:29:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.43,0:30:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- So, please.\N- Two-choice quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.33,0:30:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.53,0:30:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then answer with A or B.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.20,0:30:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My father passed away a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.48,0:30:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, who was the comedian who came to my house, offered incense, and sobbed with his hands together in front of the Buddhist altar?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.99,0:30:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.30,0:30:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada Masatoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.16,0:30:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,B:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.93,0:30:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,MASATOSHI HAMADA
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.78,0:30:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me .
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.01,0:30:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally get the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.02,0:30:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.75,0:30:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally get the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.75,0:31:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to understand than the previous quizzes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.46,0:31:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, second question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.09,0:31:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.26,0:31:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking of a question now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.50,0:31:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the sound of a bush warbler?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A:
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.27,0:31:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ho - Hokekyo"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.34,0:31:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B:
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mister...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.75,0:31:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mister, thank you so much for everything..!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.12,0:31:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.83,0:31:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mister, Mister, thank you so much for everything...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.26,0:31:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.\NWhat the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.53,0:31:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is all me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.64,0:31:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Third question.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.80,0:31:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.01,0:31:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's enough.\N- What did Gagarin say when he saw the earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.21,0:31:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is a good question, right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.68,0:32:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A:  "The earth is blue."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,B:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.02,0:32:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why did you die, Mister!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.52,0:32:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mister!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.06,0:32:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!!
